      "content": "idk i don't really want to go to a hospital if i can help it. it's so expensive and honestly it just feels like my heart is racing and i'm out of breath from the flight stress. are you sure it's not just a panic attack? if i just take some calming meds or try to relax, it'll probably go away on its own right?",
